Simple experiment base on Loren Segal tutorial about creating a new languague with Bison, Flex, and LLVM
http://gnuu.org/2009/09/18/writing-your-own-toy-compiler/all/1/

Original project can be found here
https://github.com/lsegal/my_toy_compiler

Directory structure
docs:	LLVM tutorial and presentation, AST UML, doxygen, etc...
src:	Source code



Ps: Some information on using git through proxys
http://anilattech.wordpress.com/2011/07/27/git-behind-proxy/
